{"tid":185882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟夢既內容係咪真係有隱藏意思","createTime":"2017-04-03T18:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T14:44:03.000Z","uid":45164,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96dc9ffad84d0bf2a2c2f767b16e783763b13e33","tid":185882,"uid":45164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:48:28.000Z","msg":"最近發多咗夢<br />\n但都係一啲奇奇怪怪既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實發夢既內容係咪代表住將來會發生既野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78abb40bdd78770ab6b4ebaf768925db0d20609","tid":185882,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"我聽過既講法係夢係由記憶的碎片砌成的"},{"pid":"1dbe208080d3ff39e0f6d50bb4ace746ce40bfd9","tid":185882,"uid":44068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:56:13.000Z","msg":"你講出黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b202dfbf294ab285ddebd947780607859f8d944","tid":185882,"uid":69604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:11:33.000Z","msg":"有意思 但唔係啲咩預知夢 樓主可以上網睇下 發咩夢 有咩意思 通常個排發某啲夢 代表你個啲心情 狀態 例如甩牙 好多時話你無信心 好似係"},{"pid":"77980250f100e1bca8080e52e417822ad9b75cf9","tid":185882,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9em4uJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9em4uJ.jpg&h=425b69ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4QBL7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4QBL7G.jpg&h=4258d146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c24ec233717628c01dc1716c7f2f2b93b617429","tid":185882,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"965c0a0c0d41bdece33ce2e2c729529fa8cfdce0","tid":185882,"uid":60611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:37:21.000Z","msg":"夢係潛意識想帶比你既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n潛意識會透過夢去滿足你既欲望又或者向你表達啲你前意識同意識唔應該接受既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeefda888ead8278d11a840e71cc3d70a6f7f510","tid":185882,"uid":95741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:22:21.000Z","msg":"我聽人講發夢係因為你腦部重整緊記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139dac0bddd13eb82c3ddddca24252d87d99404c","tid":185882,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有意思 但唔係啲咩預知夢 樓主可以上網睇下 發咩夢 有咩意思 通常個排發某啲夢 代表你個啲心情 狀態 例如甩牙 好多時話你無信心 好似係</blockquote><br />\n我日日啲牙都勁痛，甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6d8bda1ab6fcc5662eafb8ce36101498824dcc","tid":185882,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"我琴晚夢到外星人打地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cf8f37d4a7149239aef47e8514118706d91218","tid":185882,"uid":45164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講出黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b952ba4ef95e6254f8934c079e0a6905341d10","tid":185882,"uid":102835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"夢的解析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夢係我地潛意識建構出黎去滿足我地一啲欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時發啲夢真係爽到笑著醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好多時都係啲無厘頭片段嘅夢，有時仲會重覆發同一個夢<br />\n有壓力或心情唔好個陣好易發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包括俾人追殺呀被打被屈見鬼之類<br />\n之前都睇過本書話依啲象徵係有得解但唔知可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> e.g. 被追打係現實中你要做一樣好緊迫但未準備好嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d6b879a9dee67885fba4a7d1ada912fccad73a","tid":185882,"uid":18944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"夢見未見過嘅異性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9251fc1677e56d0c6643261c9aecb441a2014133","tid":185882,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你講出黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbf5204d1bd251fc24be7e3113a5ef21562212c","tid":185882,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"上youtube睇潛行空間 解説<br />\n有條台灣講得高質"},{"pid":"44b3a92d697c476a97abaecf91078f24864e4068","tid":185882,"uid":23277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7b2ce9a1fdf3e57beacc77709c03b7bc2a859186","tid":185882,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你講出黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783e4d2c1030b4f7455b6014bc682d161a84d04e","tid":185882,"uid":45164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你講出黎